lead_paragraph: Colby Rasmus hit a tie-breaking grand slam in the fifth inning to lead the Houston Astros to an 8-3 win over the Boston Red Sox on Saturday that snapped a four-game skid.

headline.print_headline: Grand Slam, 5 RBIs by Rasmus Helps Astros Over Red Sox 8-3
